{"id": "1244942866480889968", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "所以唯一的種子好用嗎？", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T09:18:29.289000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1244951819072049162", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "274888866941501442", "author_name": "wuboying.", "author_bot": false, "content": "我覺得種子要看隊伍，然後取決自己隊伍的打法看這張要早用還晚用。\n早用：適用於麻毒隊（不是毒隊）或者需要墊牌的隊伍，至少確保整個隊伍有3.4張你覺得能用的技能。\n晚用：翻盤用，最好是拖到有一定回合算力且主力活其它能躺就躺，以高傷害牌反撲。比方莉枝氦閃和尤烏尖嘯。", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T09:54:03.753000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1244952458187505758", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "274888866941501442", "author_name": "wuboying.", "author_bot": false, "content": "比較其它的就屬臨機應變，比如看到毒妃就種子抓淨化，看到打擊手抓麻痺哪怕傷害不高。", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T09:56:36.130000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1244970896888823831", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "種子不錯但超強且比他穩定的鑰令太多，主要他也有一定的RNG，不是用資訊／不平等拿出來未到要值得佔一個鑰令位。", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T11:09:52.259000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1244973935980711989", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "我在想機車旋轉妹的命運工匠刷牌給希洛棄和棄完之後用復製牌補回手牌。然後機車妹爆發有全隊強化挺適合希洛用。", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T11:21:56.835000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["274888866941501442"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1244600788941017108", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
